-04-02T09:02:47.000Z","msg":"因為係共產黨統治下，人權地位最低"},{"pid":"8e163bff230472a219fbd868d1ce78c229b64a7b","tid":1955003,"uid":247032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1939d61468f63b0ab06ce209b63d503b9a5196a2","tid":1955003,"uid":37869,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"249d688d9b99508158182177657b54a732992529","tid":1955003,"uid":188176,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T08:11:42.000Z","msg":"佢咁講得係唔係預比人上訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基本法係無上權力<br />\n法官都無權力違反wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T08:18:29.000Z","msg":"之前好似講過自由唔係無上限<br />\n例如而家以「防疫」之名凌駕左集會自由<br />\n法官亦可以以「預防恐怖主義」之名凌駕人權<br />\n條文係就係咁寫<br />\n但條文應該點理解 除左人大之外 就係由法官去解讀<br />\n簡單黎講就係法官話係咁就係咁<br />\n700萬香港人對條文的理解同法官唔同又點？<br />\n法官話係咁樣就係咁<br />\n<br />\n外國的法官雖然制度上係一樣<br />\n外國的法官係為人民服務 所以唔會違反人民的期望<br />\n而香港的法官係為中國共產黨服務<br />\n自然會盡量符合中國共產黨的期望<br />\n冇一個法官係無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T09:03:15.000Z","msg":"爸打一針見血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12df4b5765f375776ec110bcd3108925f704ccae","tid":1955003,"uid":134087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b83a20e38388ec6136daaa64199f0c6d47c0472b","tid":1955003,"uid":84394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75a31458d7c0d1d823a027af7bb2b772e54ab442","tid":1955003,"uid":188282,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T08:10:35.000Z","msg":"咁判詞有冇規定受害人要俾密碼?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T08:41:50.000Z","msg":"唔記得左點比喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T09:03:51.000Z","msg":"盜竊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收手機做證物<br />\n再明正言順攞搜查爆手機<br />\n唔識咪害人 講多錯多"},{"pid":"5bf906530f43679a7cfe